      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述节拍累加器的工作逻辑。核心是两个状态：ACCUMULATE和OUTPUT。系统启动后先进入ACCUMULATE状态收集窄节拍。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "OUTPUT",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，启动节点指向ACCUMULATE。那状态转换条件是什么？什么情况下从ACCUMULATE转到OUTPUT？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "OUTPUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有两个条件：当beat计数达到RATIO-1时，或者这是最后一个节拍（LAST）时，就要转到OUTPUT状态输出宽节拍。另外如果还没满，beat小于RATIO-1的话，就继续留在ACCUMULATE自循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "OUTPUT",
        "beat",
        "RATIO-1",
        "LAST"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了状态转换：ACCUMULATE自循环标注beat < RATIO-1，到OUTPUT的转换标注beat == RATIO-1 or LAST。那OUTPUT之后怎么回到ACCUMULATE？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "OUTPUT",
        "m_ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "OUTPUT输出完成后，当m_ready信号有效时就回到ACCUMULATE，开始下一轮收集。另外给两个状态加个注释说明：ACCUMULATE是\"Collecting narrow beats into buffer\"，OUTPUT是\"Buffer full, Output wide beat\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OUTPUT",
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "m_ready",
        "buffer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加OUTPUT到ACCUMULATE的转换，条件m_ready。注释也加上了，放在两个状态右侧。我检查一下：启动→ACCUMULATE，累加逻辑，满或最后则输出，输出完就绪再回去。结构应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "OUTPUT",
        "m_ready",
        "note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
